                <h2>Clinical Treatments — Jab Natural Remedies Enough Na Hon</h2>
                <p>Natural remedies spreading slow karti hain, lekin agar greying aggressive hai ya bahut advance stage mein hai — toh clinical treatments significantly better results dete hain. DenceSpot Clinic Gurgaon mein ye advanced treatments available hain:</p>

                <h3>PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) Therapy</h3>
                <p><a href="prp-hair-treatment-natural-way-to-regrow-hair.php">PRP treatment</a> mein aapke apne blood se growth factors extract karke scalp mein inject kiye jaate hain. Ye growth factors <strong>dormant melanocytes ko re-activate</strong> kar sakte hain. Research dikhati hai ki PRP melanocyte proliferation aur migration ko stimulate karta hai. 4-6 sessions (monthly intervals) mein noticeable improvement dikhti hai. Ye <a href="../hair-prp-treatment-in-gurgaon">DenceSpot ka most popular anti-greying treatment</a> hai.</p>

                <h3>Growth Factor Therapy</h3>
                <p>Concentrated growth factors directly scalp mein deliver kiye jaate hain. Ye melanocyte stem cells ko nourish karte hain aur unki lifespan extend karte hain. PRP ke saath combine karne se results aur better hote hain.</p>

                <h3>Mesotherapy for Anti-Greying</h3>
                <p>Mesotherapy mein vitamins, minerals, amino acids, aur peptides ka cocktail micro-injections se scalp mein deliver hota hai. Ye directly melanocytes tak nutrients pahunchata hai — oral supplements se kahin zyada effective hai kyunki absorption 100% hoti hai. Copper peptides, Vitamin B complex, aur biotin typically include kiye jaate hain.</p>

                <h3>LED Light Therapy</h3>
                <p>Specific wavelengths ki red aur near-infrared light melanocyte function ko stimulate kar sakti hai. Ye non-invasive hai, painless hai, aur PRP ke saath complement ke taur pe use hoti hai. Weekly sessions se cumulative results milte hain.</p>

                <h2>Anti-Greying Supplements — Kya Kaam Karte Hain?</h2>
                <p>Market mein bahut se "anti-grey" supplements available hain. Kaunse actually evidence-backed hain?</p>

                <p><strong>Catalase supplements:</strong> Catalase enzyme hydrogen peroxide ko neutralize karta hai. Some studies suggest ki supplementation se greying slow ho sakti hai. <strong>PABA (Para-Aminobenzoic Acid):</strong> Ek B-vitamin complex jo kuch studies mein greying reverse karne mein helpful paya gaya. <strong>Copper supplements:</strong> Sirf tab lein jab blood test mein copper deficiency confirm ho — excess copper toxic hai. <strong>Fo-Ti (He Shou Wu):</strong> Chinese medicine mein centuries se use hota hai anti-greying ke liye. Some preliminary research supports its role. <strong>Biotin + B12 combination:</strong> Ye dono milke melanin production pathway ko support karte hain.</p>

                <p><strong>Important warning:</strong> Koi bhi supplement bina doctor ki salah ke mat lein. Over-supplementation harmful ho sakta hai. DenceSpot mein hum blood reports dekh ke specific supplement plan recommend karte hain.</p>

                <h2>Realistic Timeline — Kya Expect Karein Aur Kab</h2>
                <p>Honesty se baat karein toh — <strong>already safed ho chuke baal wapas kaale hona bahut rare hai</strong>. Lekin <a href="can-white-hair-turn-black-again.php">kya white hair wapas black ho sakte hain</a> — ye sawal ka jawaab complicated hai. Kuch cases mein possible hai, lekin majority mein focus hona chahiye spreading rokne pe.</p>

                <p><strong>Month 1-2:</strong> Diet changes aur supplements ka effect body mein build hona shuru hota hai. Natural remedies se scalp health improve hoti hai. Clinical treatments start karein toh initial response dikhna shuru hota hai.</p>

                <p><strong>Month 3-4:</strong> New hair growth mein pigment retention better dikhta hai. Spreading ki speed slow honi chahiye. Scalp health mein noticeable improvement. Blood reports mein deficiencies correct hona shuru hoti hain.</p>

                <p><strong>Month 5-6:</strong> Consistent approach follow kiya hai toh spreading significantly slow ho chuki hogi. PRP ke results clearly visible hote hain. Some people report naye baalon mein darker pigment.</p>

                <p><strong>Month 6+:</strong> Maintenance phase — results sustain karne ke liye. Quarterly PRP sessions. Continued dietary discipline. Natural remedies as ongoing support.</p>

                <p>Ye samajhein — greying ek <strong>ongoing process</strong> hai. Isko "cure" nahi kiya ja sakta, lekin definitely <strong>slow aur manage</strong> kiya ja sakta hai. Jo log consistent rehte hain, unke results dramatically better hote hain un logon se jo 1-2 month try karke chhod dete hain.</p>

